1.0.name: wordpress/device-theme-switcher
1.0.description: Device Theme Switcher is a WordPress plugin which delivers one of your WordPress themes to handheld visitors and another theme to tablet visitors. Computer visitors are given the active theme in 'Appearance > Themes'.
